<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
<literal>repvec </literal> repeat <emphasis role="bold">m</emphasis> times the vector <emphasis role="bold">x</emphasis> in
the form <emphasis role="bold">y(1:m,:)=x</emphasis>.
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

